na, to distinguish him from another of the same name (  Simon Zelotes ). ‘When Jesus beheld him, he said, Thou art Simon the son of Jona: thou shalt be called Cephas, which is by interpretation, A stone’ (John 1:42). According to Matthew 16:17–18, Christ says more explicitly, ‘Blessed art thou, Simon Bar-jona … thou art Peter, and upon this rock I will build my church’. The name has been in continuous use since the Middle Ages."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Peter af Spurila was born about 1180, in Spurila, Turku ja Pori, Finland. He married Mrs. Peter. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter."},"et":{"Abt 1180–":"umbes 1180–Surnud","1190–Female":"1190–Surnud","1200–1265":"1200–1265","1180–Male":"1180–Surnud","1190":"1190","Abt 1200":"umbes 1200","1200":"1200","1265":"1265","Abt 1180":"umbes 1180","1180":"1180","Spurila, Pyhämaa, Turku Pori, Finland":"Spurila, Turku ja Pori, Soome"},"fi":{"Abt 1180–":"noin 1180–Kuollut","1190–Female":"1190–Kuollut","1200–1265":"1200–1265","1180–Male":"1180–Kuollut","1190":"1190","Abt 1200":"noin 1200","1200":"1200","1265":"1265","Abt 1180":"noin 1180","1180":"1180","Spurila, Pyhämaa, Turku Pori, Finland":"Spurila, Turku ja Pori, Suomi"},"fr":{"Abt 1180–":"environ 1180–Décédé","1190–Female":"1190–Décédée","1200–1265":"1200–1265","1180–Male":"1180–Décédé","1190":"1190","Abt 1200":"environ 1200","1200":"1200","1265":"1265","Abt 1180":"environ 1180","1180":"1180","Spurila, Pyhämaa, Turku Pori, Finland":"Spurila, Turku ja Pori, Finlande","lifeSummary":"Peter af Spurila est né environ 1180, à Spurila, Turku ja Pori, Finlande. Il a épousé Mrs. Peter. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fille."},"de":{"Abt 1180–":"um 1180–Verstorben","1190–Female":"1190–Verstorben","1200–1265":"1200–1265","1180–Male":"1180–Verstorben","1190":"1190","Abt 1200":"um 1200","1200":"1200","1265":"1265","Abt 1180":"um 1180","1180":"1180","Spurila, Pyhämaa, Turku Pori, Finland":"Spurila, Turku ja Pori, Finnland","lifeSummary":"Peter af Spurila wurde um 1180 in Spurila, Tu